---
title: Peppercorn Gravy Beef Strips with Garlic Veggies & Potato Mash
description: Pep up this new take on beef, veggies and mash with a sensational peppercorn gravy. There’s no need for anything fancy, it’s as simple as adding the gravy to the peppered beef and voila, you now have a delectable addition to your dinner!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
